INSERT INTO `cms_page_versions` VALUES (43,20,'en','Managed IT','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Managed IT </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All the network services you need organized into levels that fit your business. Choose the one that works for you. All of them include the following: </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Network Monitoring with ABSS ClearView </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;ve ever looked at a rack of servers (or even just stood next to a desktop computer), you&rsquo;ve likely noticed how difficult it is to tell that, say, a critical hard drive is on its last legs. After all, if it isn&rsquo;t making crunchy grinding noises, it&rsquo;s &ldquo;likely&rdquo; doing just fine. Banking on &ldquo;likely&rdquo; is similar to rolling the dice. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you could see inside, things might look a little clearer (and you won&rsquo;t have to gamble). </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Our ClearView monitoring lets us do exactly that. It&rsquo;s a window to the inner workings of your network. With it we can: </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Communicate with a secure, invisible connection </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;All transmissions to and from your network are encrypted via SSL. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;The monitoring agent uses almost no system resources. You will not see any </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">network slow-downs. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Manage and monitor Servers, Networks and Workstations </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ Choose the plan that&rsquo;s right for you. We can cover one server or an entire network </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— Find problems before they happen<br /> â—‹ ClearView checks the operation of your equipment against known baselines. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Hardware failure is usually preceded by small changes in operation. We get </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">notified the instant that happens. </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Fix many problems without coming in </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ ClearView and our Managed IT service includes remote repair when possible. Most remote services don&rsquo;t need a person on your end at all. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Keep antivirus up-to-date on all your machines<br /> â—‹ It&rsquo;s not likely that all your employees think to maintain their own machines. Some </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">might. We make sure all computers are protected. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Keep everything patched </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ Program updates are regular events. It&rsquo;s hard enough to keep track when you use two programs on three machines. Many of our customers have tens of programs on hundreds of computers. We update them all. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Track the inventory and age of your hardware </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;We catalog the hardware in each machine. If something needs to be replaced, </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">we&rsquo;ll know what it is without interrupting your day. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;You are informed when equipment is going out of warranty. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Maintain software license agreements </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;Program installations are tracked. If you get close to exceeding allotted seats, we </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">will let you know. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;We&rsquo;ll track illegal software downloads. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— &nbsp;Generate a report </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ Since our monitoring is mostly invisible, we document our activity and supply it in a monthly, easy-to-read report. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call the Help Desk </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Sometimes all you want is an e-mail account for a new salesperson. This is the sort of thing we handle in minutes. All you need to do is request it. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Maybe an employee forgot a password and entered the wrong one too many times. They&rsquo;re locked out of their own machine and can not get any work done. We can resolve this during office hours with one quick phone call. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All our levels of service include some amount of this kind of help. We&rsquo;re like that tech-savvy friend that so many people have. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Come to think of it, we&rsquo;re also a friend of that friend. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">We&rsquo;re the Expert&rsquo;s Expert when you need one </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Here&rsquo;s where things get interesting (or complicated, if you&rsquo;re not a computer person at heart). Could be you have a flat ethernet network with 524 end-users and a few server farms. The network performance is poor from time to time and you&rsquo;re not sure what to do next. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">You&rsquo;ve asked your in-house IT to do analysis and possibly redesign the current infrastructure to improve performance. Your employee is top-notch and usually takes any problem and<br /> just handles it. This time, however, the initial response to your request was an expression of excitement that slowly degenerated into abject terror. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Your IT experts have not kept up with technology. They&rsquo;re not sure what to do next, either. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Of course this scenario is quite a bit better than having an under-qualified, over-confident staff member just diving in and hoping they can swim. It takes training, experience, and life-long learning to avoid drowning in an ocean of routers, cables, switches, and CPUs. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">This is another reason we&rsquo;re here &ndash; to be your IT expert&rsquo;s expert. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Maybe your network slow-down problem stems from too many data collisions. It&rsquo;s possible that segmentation is the answer. We need to start by taking a look inside. The best thing to do right now is call us at ###-###-#### to find out for sure. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Levels of Service </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â— </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Platinum Support: </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;Weekly Network Server Health Check, Analysis &amp; Reporting </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;Microsoft Service Pack &amp; Security Patch Notifications </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ &nbsp;Unlimited Remote Voice 