rdware. Your ABSS DataVault has no footprint and can be setup up in minutes. Once the initial backup has been made, the rest can be incremental. Only the changes get saved and the draw on your network is nearly undetectable. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call today and protect your data </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: &lt;cms:phone /&gt;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-03-21 23:03:01','2012-03-21 23:03:01','2012-03-21 23:03:01'),(117,30,'en','Disaster & Recovery Planning','<h1>Disaster &amp; Recovery Planning</h1>\r\n<p>Content Needed</p>','1','2012-03-21 23:04:30','2012-03-21 23:04:30','2012-03-21 23:04:30'),(118,22,'en','Network Security Auditing','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; float: right;\" src=\"../../../../app/assets/images/sitting-laptop.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" />Network Security Auditing</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you\'ve been in business long enough, you\'ll likely agree that people will try to hack your network, you know, just because. They&rsquo;ll write programs that target indiscriminately. They&rsquo;ll set up scripts that tirelessly chip away at your passwords. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">One day they&rsquo;ll get through and your data will be compromised.<br /> If you have nothing to hide, intrusions are still disasters waiting to happen.<br /> If you have something to hide, like customer data, intrusions are lawsuits waiting to happen. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Hardware Firewalls </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Keep malicious content from entering or leaving your network. Once it gets in, it often takes hold and starts sending sensitive material out. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;ve got anything worth protecting, running without security has a horrible risk/reward ratio. You are risking everything for a reward of nothing. Turn the tables with one easy step. Add a hardware firewall and lock down your data. Change the ratio so you can risk nothing to keep everything. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Call ABSS at ###-###-#### to put your data behind the firewall and keep it safe. It&rsquo;s simple to do and it just makes good sense. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Patch Management </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Updating operating systems, virus protection, and software on one machine is mildly time- consuming at best. If you&rsquo;ve got 342 machines, it&rsquo;s certainly too much for one person to maintain all of them. It&rsquo;s probably too much to expect even 342 people to maintain one machine a piece. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Avoiding lost time by simply not having it often costs more money than it saves. Patches, especially those for operating systems and virus protection, are written to solve security issues. Since some people are constantly finding new ways to break in to your network, other people are constantly working to keep those intruders out. Their work is distributed as a patch. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Sign up for patch management from ABSS NetSecure. Every machine gets kept up-to-date. You avoid lost time because we do all the work. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Vulnerability Testing and Assessment </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Threats come from outside and inside your network. Even if you have a firewall and patch management in place, you are constantly visible to intruders. They may not be able to get in at this moment, but they&rsquo;re always looking toward the next. This means it&rsquo;s good practice to test your security at regular intervals. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Firewalls only work as well as they&rsquo;re configured. That configuration must be updated to keep up with emerging threats. One update might be a simple change to one setting. But if your administrator allows incomplete updates to stack up, they&rsquo;ll end up with a complicated task in </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">a short period of time. If that administrator is replaced and leaves no documentation, the new person may not even know where to start. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Entrust our ABSS NetSecure professionals to test your firewall configuration for vulnerabilities and advise or implement a solution if they are found. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Inside threats are different. They often get placed when someone finds a way to get them through the firewall. Malicious software can sit dormant for days or months and then activate on command. The key to preventing an outbreak throughout the network, or even a little data stream from heading out into the world, is containment. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Unfortunately, it&rsquo;s difficult to spot dormant threats (they are often stealthy by design). Fortunately, our tests confirm that when they become active, they won&rsquo;t be allowed to go anywhere. Our efficiency allows us to test every machine on your network while your people continue to work. When a threat comes to life, it will open its eyes to an impenetrable cage. After that, if you&rsquo;ve signed up for Managed IT, we&rsquo;ll spot it with ABSS ClearView and take it out. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call today and protect your network </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: &lt;cms:phone /&gt;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-03-21 23:05:14','2012-03-21 23:05:14','2012-03-21 23:05:14'),(119,31,'en','DataCenter Hosting','<h1>DataCenter Hosting</h1>','1','2012-03-21 23:06:34','2012-03-21 23:06:34','2012-03-21 23:06:34'),(120,31,'en','DataCenter Hosting','<h1>DataCenter Hosting</h1>\r\n<p>Content Needed</p>','1','2012-03-21 23:06:50','2012-03-21 23:06:50','2012-03-21 23:06:50'),(121,20,'en','Managed & Field IT Services','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"float: right; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"../../../../app/assets/images/man-rack.jpg\" alt=\"\" />Managed IT</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All the network services you need organized into levels that fit your business. Choose the one that works for you. All of them include the following: </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Network Monitoring with ABSS ClearView </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;ve ever looked at a rack of servers (or even just stood next to a desktop computer), you&rsquo;ve likely noticed how difficult it is to tell that, say, a critical hard drive is on its last legs. After all, if it isn&rsquo;t making crunchy grinding noises, it&rsquo;s &ldquo;likely&rdquo; doing just fine. Banking on &ldquo;likely&rdquo; is similar to rolling the dice. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you could see inside, things might look a little clearer (and you won&rsquo;t have to gamble). </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Our ClearView monitoring lets us do exactly that. It&rsquo;s a window to the inner workings of your network. With it we can: </span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Communicate with a secure, invisible connection</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All transmissions to and from your network are encrypted via SSL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">The monitoring agent uses almost no system resources. You will not see any&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">network slow-downs.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Manage and monitor Servers, Networks and Workstations</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Choose the plan that&rsquo;s right for you. We can cover one server or an entire network</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Find problems before they happen</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">ClearView checks the operation of your equipment against known baselines.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Hardware failure is usually preceded by small changes in operation. We get&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">notified the instant that happens.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Fix many problems without coming in</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">ClearView and our Managed IT service includes remote repair when possible. Most remote services don&rsquo;t need a person on your end at all.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Keep antivirus up-to-date on all your machines</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">It&rsquo;s not likely that all your employees think to maintain their own machines. Some&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">might. We make sure all computers are protected.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Keep everything patched</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">P</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">rogram updates are regular events. It&rsquo;s hard enough to keep track when you use two programs on three machines. Many of our customers have tens of programs on hundreds of computers. We update them all.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Track the inventory and age of your hardware</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\"><br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">We catalog the hardware in each machine. If something needs to be replaced,</span></li>\r\n<li>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">we&rsquo;ll know what it is without interrupting your day. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12; &nbsp;You are informed when equipment is going out of warranty. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12; &nbsp;Maintain software license agreements </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12; &nbsp;Program installations are tracked. If you get close to exceeding allotted seats, we </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">will let you know. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12; &nbsp;We&rsquo;ll track illegal software downloads. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12; &nbsp;Generate a report </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12; Since our monitoring is mostly invisible, we document our activity and supply it in a monthly, easy-to-read report. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call the Help Desk </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Sometimes all you want is an e-mail account for a new salesperson. This is the sort of thing we handle in minutes. All you need to do is request it. </sp