ource=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=1185+Hugh+Allan+Drive,+Kamloops,+BC,+Canada&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=1185+hugh+allan+drive+Kamlo&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=38.144864,84.638672&amp;t=h&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=1185+Hugh+Allan+Dr,+Kamloops,+British+Columbia+V1S+1M8,+Canada&amp;ll=50.657025,-120.369387&amp;spn=0.019045,0.036564&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A\">View Larger Map</a></small></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','1','2012-07-29 22:54:51','2012-07-29 22:54:51','2012-07-29 22:54:51'),(169,46,'en','Design','<h2>Website Design</h2>\r\n<p>Your business\' face to the internet world is a very important one. With an outdated website, you can convey a lot of mixed messages of professionalism. Our skilled designers can create a design unique to your needs, providing features specific to your industry.</p>\r\n<h2>Mobile Websites</h2>\r\n<p>Are you trying to reach mobile users? A complex website design can be too large or improperly scaled for the mobile platforms. Tested against iPhone, Android and BlackBerry devices, we will ensure that your website looks good and provides users with the information they need.</p>','1','2012-07-29 23:06:18','2012-07-29 23:06:18','2012-07-29 23:06:18'),(170,49,'en','Develop','<h2>Content Management System</h2>\r\n<p>The basis of most of our websites, a Content Management System (CMS) allows clents to manage their website pages and other data. Without having to go through a programmer or design company, content can be changed in seconds and requires no additional hourly fees.</p>\r\n<h2>Additional Modules</h2>\r\n<p>Managing your website page content is just the beginning, more custom applications can be integrated in your website. If you are looking for a <strong>blog</strong>, <strong>e-commerce store</strong>, or <strong>real estate listings manager</strong>, these features and more can be added.</p>\r\n<h2>Social Media Applications</h2>\r\n<p>Integrate with social media on a whole new scale. Create Facebook tabs, mobile events, and more:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Facebook Contests, Quizzes, Voting, Image Uploading</li>\r\n<li>Promotion Code Generation and Tracking</li>\r\n<li>Text Messaging (SMS) Events and Notifications</li>\r\n<li>Twitter, Facebook, and LinkedIn Integration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Custom Application Development</h2>\r\n<p>Go above and beyond a website and make a web application.</p>\r\n<p>If you have business processes that require automation or a system users could re-use, we can create it.</p>','1','2012-07-29 23:08:20','2012-07-29 23:08:20','2012-07-29 23:08:20'),(171,49,'en','Develop','<h2>Content Management System</h2>\r\n<p>The basis of most of our websites, a Content Management System (CMS) allows clents to manage their website pages and other data. Without having to go through a programmer or design company, content can be changed in seconds and requires no additional hourly fees.</p>\r\n<h2>Additional Modules</h2>\r\n<p>Managing your website page content is just the beginning, more custom applications can be integrated in your website. If you are looking for a <strong>blog</strong>, <strong>e-commerce store</strong>, or <strong>real estate listings manager</strong>, these features and more can be added.</p>\r\n<h2>Social Media Applications</h2>\r\n<p>Integrate with social media on a whole new scale. Create Facebook tabs, mobile events, and more:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Facebook Contests, Quizzes, Voting, Image Uploading</li>\r\n<li>Promotion Code Generation and Tracking</li>\r\n<li>Text Messaging (SMS) Events and Notifications</li>\r\n<li>Twitter, Facebook, and LinkedIn Integration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Custom Application Development</h2>\r\n<p>Go above and beyond a website and make a web application.</p>\r\n<p>If you have business processes that require automation or a system users could re-use, we can create it.</p>','1','2012-07-29 23:08:42','2012-07-29 23:08:42','2012-07-29 23:08:42'),(172,50,'en','Deploy','<h2>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h2>\r\n<p>After performing keyword research for your industry, we will be able to target terms that potential customers.</p>\r\n<h2>Pay-Per-Click (PPC) Marketing</h2>\r\n<p>Want to get customers or conversions quickly? Alongside the SEO research, we can target these terms with paid ads and get your website ranked among the top results. The beautiful part: You only spend money if they click, resulting in visitors that actually want to see your content.</p>\r\n<h2>Social Media Integration</h2>\r\n<p>Don\'t have time to update your social networks? We can create campaigns involving the masses to get you more exposure in the social streams, as well as get your community involved with your business.</p>\r\n<h2>Analytics and Reporting</h2>\r\n<p>Find out how people are getting to your website and improve the lower performing pages. Create special landing pages unique to advertising campaigns and geared to those visitors. Get real-time reporting for the visitors of your website.</p>\r\n<p>With the various analytics tools available, you can find out what\'s going on and react to it.</p>','1','2012-07-29 23:19:31','2012-07-29 23:19:31','2012-07-29 23:19:31'),(173,51,'en','Contact','<p>Have you got a website, mobile app, or social media idea?</p>\r\n<p>We can make your dreams a reality, and it all starts with some conversation.</p>\r\n<table class=\"design\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Contact Form</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Serif\', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Fill out the following form, and we\'ll get back to you as soon as possible!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: normal;\">&lt;cms:form id=\"contact\" /&gt;</p>\r\n<h2>Mailing Address</h2>\r\n<p>Exodus Media<br />#216-1185 Hugh Allan Drive<br />Kamloops, BC<br />V1S 1T3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><iframe src=\"